    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>匆匆忙忙从这里到那里，停下来仿佛会失去自我。</p><span id="more"></span><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aplayer/dist/APlayer.min.css"><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aplayer/dist/APlayer.min.js"></script><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/meting@2/dist/Meting.min.js"></script><p>四海为家无根蒂，<br>寻觅知音难相逢。<br>漂泊无端似浮萍，<br>停留恐惧成懒惰。<br>迷茫彷徨心不安，<br>何处是我真心所？<br>或许应该放下身，<br>顺其自然随缘走。</p><p><meting-js    auto="https://music.163.com/song?id=1914105926" autoplay=false ><br></meting-js></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;匆匆忙忙从这里到那里，停下来仿佛会失去自我。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
